---
import Card from "../components/card/Card.astro";
import VideoCard from "../components/card/VideoCard.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="NURA">
  <div class="gap-3 hidden md:flex text-[#BB7A1C] text-sm font-normal">
    <p>Home</p>
    <p>/</p>
    <p>Our Technology</p>
  </div>
  <!--  -->
  <div class="md:mt-[20px] lg:mt-[50px] hidden md:block lg:max-w-[1400px]">
    <img class="lg:w-full" src="/assets/images/svg/header_img.svg" alt="" />
  </div>
  <div class="mt-5 lg:mt-[70px] block md:hidden lg:max-w-[1400px]">
    <img
      class="w-full lg:w-full"
      src="/assets/images/svg/header_sm_img.svg"
      alt=""
    />
  </div>
  <!--  -->
  <div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between mt-5 md:mt-[20px] lg:mt-[50px] gap-10">
    <div class="hidden lg:block md:shrink-2 lg:shrink-0">
      <img class="" src="/assets/images/svg/content_img_one.svg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="block lg:hidden">
      <img
        class="w-full"
        src="/assets/images/svg/content_sm_img_one.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[16px] bg-[#BBEEEF] mt-5 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-[690px]">
      <h1
        class="text-black text-2xl md:text-5xl font-semibold pt-10 lg:pt-[60px] pl-5 lg:pl-[50px] pr-5 lg:pr-10 leading-[32px] md:leading-[56px]"
      >
        Using AI technology to improve your screening experience
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-black text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px] pb-10 pl-5 lg:pl-[50px]"
      >
        At NURA, our screening experience is designed to suit your busy life.
        Our technology provides quick and accurate results, while always keeping
        your safety in mind. Our machines are minimally invasive and
        ergonomically designed to ensure that your experience is comfortable.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--  -->
  <div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between mt-5 md:mt-[20px] lg:mt-[50px] gap-10">
    <div class="rounded-[16px] bg-[#3D566A] lg:mt-0 mb-5 md:mb-0 lg:mb-0 lg:max-w-[690px]">
      <div
        class="flex items-center justify-start pt-10 lg:pt-[60px] pl-5 lg:pl-[50px] pr-5 lg:pr-10 gap-2 lg:gap-10"
      >
        <div class="w-[100px] md:w-[200px]">
          <img src="/assets/images/png/fujifilm_white_logo.png" alt="" />
        </div>
        <h1
          class="text-white text-2xl md:text-5xl font-semibold pr-5 lg:pr-10 leading-[32px] md:leading-[56px]"
        >
          AI technology
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p
        class="text-white text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px] pl-5 lg:pl-[50px]"
      >
        Artificial Intelligence is the next big step in healthcare technology,
        and Fujifilm is at the forefront of this movement. Our legacy in
        high-quality scanning and image processing allows us to train AI systems
        with decades of imaging data.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-white text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px] pb-10 pl-5 lg:pl-[50px]"
      >
        Our AI technology is improving outcomes for both the patient and the
        doctor by making the screening process safer and more accurate.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block md:shrink-2 lg:shrink-0">
      <img class="" src="/assets/images/svg/content_img_two.svg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="block lg:hidden">
      <img
        class="w-full"
        src="/assets/images/svg/content_sm_img_two.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--  -->

  <div class="mt-10 lg:mt-[70px]">
    <div class="md:flex md:justify-end hidden">
      <img class="w-full" src="/assets/images/svg/technology-img.svg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="block md:hidden">
      <img
        class="w-full"
        src="/assets/images/svg/technology_sm_img.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--  -->
  <div class="bg-[#F2F3F4] mt-10 md:mt-[70px] rounded-[16px]">
    <div
      class="pt-[15px] md:pt-[40px] pr-[17px] md:pr-[159px] pl-[25px] md:pl-[60px]"
    >
      <h3
        class="text-black text-xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-6 lg:leading-9"
      >
        Artificial Intelligence
      </h3>
      <p class="text-black text-base leading-6 font-normal md:leading-8">
        Artificial Intelligence describes the ability of computer programs and
        machines to mimic human intelligence. It can be further broken down into
        Machine Learning and Deep Learning.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="pt-[15px] md:pt-[40px] pr-[17px] md:pr-[159px] pl-[25px] md:pl-[60px]"
    >
      <h3
        class="text-black text-xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-6 lg:leading-9"
      >
        Deep Learning
      </h3>
      <p class="text-black text-base leading-6 font-normal md:leading-8">
        Deep Learning is one of the techniques within Machine Learning. It
        allows the program to use ‘artificial neural networks’ to perform a task
        repeatedly. The program learns from every cycle and modifies its
        approach a little each time to produce more accurate results. This
        technique helps our machines in reconstructing images, enhancing the
        sharpness of low-resolution scans, and in early detection of cancers.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="pt-[15px] md:pt-[40px] pr-[17px] md:pr-[159px] pl-[25px] md:pl-[60px] pb-5 lg:pb-[60px]"
    >
      <h3
        class="text-black text-xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-6 lg:leading-9"
      >
        Artificial Intelligence
      </h3>
      <p class="text-black text-base leading-6 font-normal md:leading-8">
        Artificial Intelligence describes the ability of computer programs and
        machines to mimic human intelligence. It can be further broken down into
        Machine Learning and Deep Learning.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!--  -->
  <div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between mt-5 md:mt-[20px] lg:mt-[50px] gap-10">
    <div class="block lg:hidden">
      <img
        class="w-full"
        src="/assets/images/svg/content_sm_img_three.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[16px] bg-white lg:mt-0 mb-5 lg:max-w-[800px]">
      <p
        class="text-black text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px]"
      >
        Fujifilm Healthcare’s vast data set of radiology images and decades of
        experience in the field has helped us develop advanced AI technologies
        that empower radiologists and doctors. Our AI allows them to read scans
        more efficiently and accurately, helping them make quick and intelligent
        decisions.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-black text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px]"
      >
        AI technology makes the screening process safer by allowing us to use
        ultra-low doses of radiation. Sharper images have previously only been
        possible with larger doses of radiation.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-black text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px] pb-10"
      >
        Our AI technology processes the low-dose scan and compares them to
        similar scans in Fujifilm’s vast library of imaging data. This enables
        us to sharpen the low-dose image and identify problems that would be
        missed by the naked eye.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block">
      <img
        class="w-full shrink-0"
        src="/assets/images/svg/content_img_three.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!--  -->
  <div class="flex flex-wrap lg:mt-[70px] md:flex md:justify-between gap-10">
    <Card
      img="/assets/images/svg/ultra_low_dose_scan_img.svg"
      ,
      title="Ultra Low-Dose Scan"
      ,
      body="A regular scan at ultra-low dose radiation is noisy and unclear, making it possible to overlook a problem."
    />
    <Card
      img="/assets/images/svg/high_dose_scan_img.svg"
      ,
      title="High-Dose Scan"
      ,
      body="The same scan with a higher dose of radiation reveals an abnormality."
    />
    <Card
      img="/assets/images/svg/ai_enhanced_ultra_low_dose_scan_img.svg"
      ,
      title="AI Enhanced Ultra Low-Dose Scan"
      ,
      body="Our AI technology is able to sharpen the quality of the ultra-low dose scan to assist the doctor in early detection."
    />
  </div>

  <!--  -->

  <div
    class="bg-[#19374F] rounded-[16px] mt-[70px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
      <h2
        class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-[36px] md:leading-[56px] pt-[66px] text-center"
      >
        How low is ultra-low radiation?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white pt-2 text-center text-xs md:text-lg px-[33px">
        based on lung cancer CT scan at ultra low dose (0.1mSv)
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:flex md:flex-row md:justify-center md:items-center gap-10 pt-[40px] pb-[72px]"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
        <h3 class="text-[#FAC140] text-5xl font-bold leading-[56px]">
          1/50 Lower
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-white pt-2 w-[159px] md:w-[232px] text-base text-center md:text-2xl"
        >
          radiation than regular imaging machines
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:mt-8">
        <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center items-center">
          <h3 class="text-[#FAC140] text-5xl font-bold leading-[56px]">BLR</h3>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center max-w-[25px]">
            <img
              class="w-full"
              src="/assets/images/png/blr_nyc_icon.png"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[#FAC140] text-5xl font-bold leading-[56px]">NYC</h3>
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-white pt-2 w-[159px] md:w-[232px] text-base text-center md:text-2xl"
        >
          equal to a round trip flight from Bangalore to New York
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="flex flex-wrap overflow-x-scroll md:flex md:justify-between md:items-center md:mt-[70px] gap-5"
  >
    <VideoCard
      img="/assets/images/svg/card_one_img.svg"
      body="REiLi is our AI technology that uses deep learning and Fujifilm’s extensive image processing database to detect abnormalities automatically. This helps doctors accurately recognize the affected area and reduce the time taken by radiologists to interpret the scan. "
    />
    <VideoCard
      img="/assets/images/svg/card_two_img.svg"
      body="FCT PixelShine is our Deep Learning based image processing software that improves the image quality of low-dose radiation scans. Sharper images have only been possible with high doses of radiation. FCT PixelShine enables our machines to produce a sharp, clear image even at ultra-low dose radiation."
    />
  </div>

  <div class="md:mt-[70px]">
    <div class="flex justify-between">
      <div class="bg-[#69C7CF] rounded-t-2xl">
        <h4 class="text-white text-4xl  px-[90px] lg:px-[100px] py-[36px]">CT Scan</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white hidden md:hidden lg:block">
        <h4 class="text-[#19374F] text-4xl px-[100px] py-[36px]">
          Digital Mammography
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white hidden md:hidden lg:block">
        <h4 class="text-[#19374F] text-4xl px-[100px] py-[36px]">
          Nasal Endoscopy
        </h4>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-[#69C7CF] flex justify-center items-center md:justify-between flex-col md:flex md:flex-row"
    >
      <div
        class="lg:pl-[60px] pt-[40px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:flex md:justify-start md:items-start"
      >
        <h2 class="text-white text-6xl">CT Scan</h2>
        <div class="flex gap-5 pt-4">
          <p class="text-[#19374F]">Safe</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
            <div>
              <img src="/assets/images/png/dot_icon.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#19374F]">Accurate</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
            <div>
              <img src="/assets/images/png/dot_icon.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#19374F]">20 Minutes</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- <div> -->
        <div class="pt-[40px] px-5 block md:hidden">
          <img src="/assets/images/png/ct_scan_img.png" alt="" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-white pt-4 w-[293px] md:w-[573px]">
          A computerized tomography scan, more commonly called a CT scan, allows
          doctors to see internal organs in much greater detail than a regular
          X-ray. It takes a series of X-ray images at various angles around your
          body and processes it together to create multiple cross-sectional
          images (slices) of the scanned body part.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-[40px] hidden md:block">
        <img src="/assets/images/png/ct_scan_img.png" alt="" />
      </div>
      <!-- </div> -->
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between mt-5 md:mt-[20px] lg:mt-[50px] gap-10">
    <div class="rounded-[16px] md:rounded-none">
      <img
        class="w-full rounded-[16px] md:rounded-none"
        src="/assets/images/svg/designed_to_ease_your_anxiety.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[16px] bg-[#BBEEEF] lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-[800px] mt-5">
      <h1
        class="text-black text-2xl md:text-5xl font-semibold pt-10 lg:pt-[60px] pl-5 lg:pl-[50px] pr-5 lg:pr-10 leading-[32px] md:leading-[56px]"
      >
        Designed to ease your anxiety
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-black text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px] pb-10 pl-5 lg:pl-[50px]"
      >
        Our CT scan machines are designed to make the screening process as
        comfortable as possible. Our gantry bore (the opening in the CT machine)
        is larger than other machines to reduce the feeling of claustrophobia
        and ease your anxiety.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between mt-5 md:mt-[20px] lg:mt-[50px] gap-10">
    <div class="block md:hidden rounded-[16px] md:rounded-none">
      <img
        class="w-full rounded-[16px] md:rounded-none"
        src="/assets/images/svg/the-accuracy_of_high_speed_scanning.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[16px] bg-[#FFDB83] lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-[800px] mt-5">
      <h1
        class="text-black text-2xl md:text-5xl font-semibold pt-10 lg:pt-[60px] pl-5 lg:pl-[50px] pr-5 lg:pr-10 leading-[32px] md:leading-[56px]"
      >
        The accuracy of high-speed scanning
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-black text-xs md:text-2xl font-normal leading-[18px] md:leading-9 pt-5 lg:pt-10 pr-5 lg:pr-[90px] pb-10 pl-5 lg:pl-[50px]"
      >
        Our high speed scanning means you only need to hold your breath for 7-8
        seconds. We use the latest 3D reconstruction technology that provides
        rapid coverage for an efficient and precise examination.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden md:block rounded-[16px] md:rounded-none mt-5">
      <img
        class="w-full rounded-[16px] md:rounded-none"
        src="/assets/images/svg/the-accuracy_of_high_speed_scanning.svg"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="bg-[#FAC140] rounded-xl mt-5 flex justify-center md:justify-between items-center lg:hidden"
  >
    <h1 class="p-[25px] text-white text-2xl font-semibold">
      Digital Mammography
    </h1>
    <div class="pr-3">
      <img src="/assets/images/png/down_arrow.png" alt="" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="bg-[#3D566A] rounded-xl mt-5 flex justify-between items-center lg:hidden md:justify-between"
  >
    <h1 class="p-[25px] text-white text-2xl font-semibold">Nasal Endoscopy</h1>
    <div class="pr-3">
      <img src="/assets/images/png/down_arrow.png" alt="" />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
